    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After all these years your bad dreams are back but something is terribly wrong... It's a surreal and dark nightmare but people seem to be scared and disgusted by... you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202410/extras/40629d31b1fa51a1288c091da679c971.poster.avif?t=1760115684\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202410/extras/40629d31b1fa51a1288c091da679c971.webm?t=1760115684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202410/extras/40629d31b1fa51a1288c091da679c971.mp4?t=1760115684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Only the old, sick and unable to evacuate remained in the city. Everyone else fled. Even though there are strange monsters roaming around the city, people hide strictly from you. <i>&quot;You can keep the whole city to yourself, <strong>but you are not welcome among us.</strong>&quot;</i> - This is the message that was left for you in the letter. The reason is not clear. Maybe you were simply mistaken for someone else? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202410/extras/8ca9a33a357452c0f812b10df4686221.poster.avif?t=1760115684\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202410/extras/8ca9a33a357452c0f812b10df4686221.webm?t=1760115684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202410/extras/8ca9a33a357452c0f812b10df4686221.mp4?t=1760115684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Game Features]</strong>  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unusual, surreal world that captures the atmosphere of a bad dream. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creative and amusing puzzles designed to surprise the player with their strange, yet consistent logic. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive and highly interactive world. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming, minimalist sketch-style graphics.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Outside the box&quot; point &amp; click gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original and debut soundtrack composed by Desert Fox.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202410/extras/e5b03011e5a1148554248ddab6e5f727.poster.avif?t=1760115684\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202410/extras/e5b03011e5a1148554248ddab6e5f727.webm?t=1760115684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202410/extras/e5b03011e5a1148554248ddab6e5f727.mp4?t=1760115684\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
